
Implementation of Viterbi algorithm in perl

Instructions:
perl Viterbi.pl trainingfile testfile outputfile
Example:
perl Viterbi.pl treebank.5290.train treebank.5290.test treebankoutput
Output:
Started Training
calling start probabilities
calling trans probabilities
Finished Training
Starting Testing
 Takes approximately few minutes for running on sentences
 Wait..
Finished tagging
Writing Output to file treebankoutput
Accuracy=90.317713136055%


